- **Count & Layers:** The structure consists of 8 building blocks arranged in a multi-layered configuration.
- **Spatial Relationships:**

  - Above these, there is a yellow rectangular block spanning horizontally between them.
  - On top of the yellow block are two blue cubes positioned side by side.
  - A green rectangular block is placed above and to the right of the blue cubes.
  - An orange triangular block is positioned at the topmost part of the structure.
